title: Pixel 5 Battery Health
content:
I use Accubattery to track detailed battery usage and noticed that my battery health is bad - under 90%.  It also fluctuates between 67% to around 90%.  My phone is 10 days old.
I am not sure if this is related to the other battery issues (such as the percentage not changing).
